},{"pid":"49a4f692688894394305d872df1dde6719dfb910","tid":1954542,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T02:47:23.000Z","msg":"哪怕烈火焚身，也巋然不動"},{"pid":"3c060992a45c9c3689c8c4eaaeb96dbf531fa8bc","tid":1954542,"uid":334831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09a0933f6292d2d32692dcf295863868734688e5","tid":1954542,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T02:01:43.000Z","msg":"中國疫情緩和後，各地企業展開復工措施。中國國家主席習近平今天前往浙江寧波視察，呼籲民眾要注意社交距離，不要進行過多聚集活動。考察期間有民眾邀請習近平一同坐船，不過習近平以&ldquo;人太多&rdquo;婉拒。<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n據頭條新聞今天說，浙江考察獲民眾邀坐船，習近平以&ldquo;人太多&rdquo;婉拒。<br />\n<br />\n該報道說，習近平昨到杭州西溪國家濕地公園進行考察，期間有乘坐觀光船的旅客主動向習近平問好，其後又詢問習近平要否一起坐觀光船。習近平問該旅客觀光船能坐多少人，旅客回答道6人，習近平微笑回答道他很想坐，然後望望身後一同前來考察的官員，但因&ldquo;人太多&rdquo;未能同船。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20200401-%E9%82%80%E8%AB%8B%E5%90%8C%E5%9D%906%E4%BA%BA%E5%B0%8F%E8%88%B9-%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E4%BB%A5%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%9A%E7%82%BA%E7%94%B1%E5%A9%89%E6%8B%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F20200401-%25E9%2582%2580%25E8%25AB%258B%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%259D%25906%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25B0%258F%25E8%2588%25B9-%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A4%259A%25E7%2582%25BA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E5%25A9%2589%25E6%258B%2592&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUjC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=bbad8c7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20200401-%E9%82%80%E8%AB%8B%E5%90%8C%E5%9D%906%E4%BA%BA%E5%B0%8F%E8%88%B9-%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E4%BB%A5%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%9A%E7%82%BA%E7%94%B1%E5%A9%89%E6%8B%92</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T02:48:52.000Z","msg":"習維尼係咪怕佢太重搞到隻船會沉😂"},{"pid":"8fb1dc20e9d1f6b6a00e3a175930fda964e86f2d","tid":1954542,"uid":270532,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4ed7a63edbc1f4832655fd9af23ab17b90e13702","tid":1954542,"uid":155095,"like":57,"dislike":0